      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c6bac066786290024ba7cd5"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "You're here to collect <i>what</i>??? Is this a joke?\n\n<i>Svolotsch</i>, spare me from your begging. I never asked for your help and didn't need it. I owe you nothing dear lady.",
