      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c7b3683633350903a94b55b"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "I say House Marik would have gotten you otherwise if it wasn't for my help. \n\nDr. Murad didn't remember seeing you among the rest of the kittens inside the ComStar facility at the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTheTwins],Twins]], but I did notice you back then and kept quiet. Which might have made Commander {COMMANDER.LastName} decide differently on whether to turn you over to Marik or not.",
      "branches": [
