      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ca952d10c2674ed4a17abdc"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Oh, but I do quite understand, <i>Lady Arano</i>. \n\nSee your Highness, one of my kittens is of [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreAuriganReach],Aurigan]] origin and he also recognized you when we captured and held hostage the doctor's team at the ComStar facility. ",
      "branches": [
