        "id": "9c87cbbedae69e06f2cbbc7a"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "But since I was more interested in your commander cooperating, I chose not to reveal this knowledge with anyone else... until now. \n\nEven though I hear the bounty on your lovely head is still quite big... any leads on you would be well paid. So, who's actually in debt on this exchange <i>pizdets</i>... hm?",
