        "id": "9c41d4cd0c43c0f64297faa1"
      },
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Then that makes you even more suited for what I'm going to propose. \n\nI need to get out of this company. There's nothing left here for me. Take me into your [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTortugaPirates],Kittens]]. You know that it is impossible to keep a MechWarrior caged as I've been for months. I'll repay you if necessary.",
